profile:
Oceanside Excavation is a full service excavation and bobcat company with over 20 years experience offering a wide range of residential services such as our unique smart ponds, rock walls, custom water features, landscaping and animal proof vegetable gardens. Our commercial services include general construction, labour, concrete, underground utilities, demolition, backfill, site preparation, slab prep, land clearing. We specialize in small to medium size jobs and have completed work for various home owners and commercial projects.

We pride ourselves in delivering excellent service on time and within budget. We service Vancouver Island including the following areas; Nanaimo, Ladysmith, Parksville, Qualicum Beach, Port Alberni and Courtney.
